# Machine Learning Projects 
This folder contains machine learning projects created while learning ML concepts and algorithms.

## Topics covered
- Decision Tree
- Random Forest
- Linear Regression
- Logistic Regression 
- Model evaluation
- Data preprocessing
- Klassification 
- KNN 
- Clustering

### Libraries used:
- Pandas
- Numpy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

Each projects contains:
- Jupyter Notebook
- Visualisations 
- Model evaluation
